OL,3,CTidal energy generator to be tested in
OL,4,Cgroundbreaking trial
OL,6,FA tidal energy generator has arrived
OL,7,Fin Alderney ahead of a landmark trial,
OL,8,Fwhich could allow the island to begin
OL,9,Futilising the untapped power source.
OL,11,FSpiralis Energy will trial its energy
OL,12,Fgenerator in the Alderney Race: a
OL,13,Fpowerful stretch of water between the
OL,14,Fisland and France that can flow as
OL,15,Ffast as 12 knots or 14 miles an hour.
OL,17,FThe trial is expected to take place in
OL,18,FApril or May 2025.
