OL,3,CTidal energy generator to be tested in
OL,4,Cgroundbreaking trial
OL,6,FSpiralis hopes the generator may be
OL,7,Fone of three devices needed to provide
OL,8,Fenough energy for the entire island.
OL,10,FThe Axial Skeltor is made from
OL,11,Frecycled plastic, only uses one moving
OL,12,Fpart, and can be repaired locally with
OL,13,F3D-printed parts.
OL,15,FThe power-generating screw is rotated
OL,16,Fby the tides to create energy and is
OL,17,Fmade to survive 25 years at sea.
