OL,3,CTidal energy generator to be tested in
OL,4,Cgroundbreaking trial
OL,6,FGuy Levene, from Spiralis, said: "The
OL,7,FAlderney Race is the perfect stage to
OL,8,Fdemonstrate the immense potential of
OL,9,Ftidal energy, a resource that is not
OL,10,Fonly sustainable but entirely reliable.
OL,12,F"Alderney represents the future of
OL,13,Fwhat's possible, and we're proud to
OL,14,Fpioneer an energy transformation with
OL,15,Fthe support of the island's community."
OL,17,FPoliticians also spoke of how the
OL,18,Fgenerators could be a gamechanger for
OL,19,Ffuture energy production.
