OL,3,CTidal energy generator to be tested in
OL,4,Cgroundbreaking trial
OL,6,FAlderney States member Alex Snowdon
OL,7,Fsays: "This might be the start of many
OL,8,Fother companies who could come to the
OL,9,Fisland.
OL,11,F"The more that is spent on tidal
OL,12,Fenergy development, the better it is
OL,13,Ffor Alderney as our asset is there. If
OL,14,Fit's Spiralis or another company, it's
OL,15,Freally important for us to unlock that
OL,16,Ftidal power generation."
